@pengys5 This relates to the service dependency tree. If an exit span is set the feedback, a field (isPeerTraced) is **Boolean** set value true, which means the peer node is being traced. So collector can ignore the relationship between the exit service and the entry service, because the peer will build this relationship by ref and entry. Otherwise, collector build the dependency relationship between these two.
